{"tid":826417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【剛力彩芽有份嗎？】前澤友作膺全球首位SpaceX太空旅客","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T11:48:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"daec5de9131c7680df12cc31f7b6685e3e5ca4be","tid":826417,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://kenshin.hk/blog/jdnews/201804/20180426-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkenshin.hk%2Fblog%2Fjdnews%2F201804%2F20180426-2.jpg&h=6cd40d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空探索技術公司SpaceX的創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）昨日在洛杉磯總部舉行記者會，正式宣布坐擁40億美元（約312億港元）身家的日本Zozotown購物網站42歲社長前澤友作，將會成為首位乘坐BFR超級火箭的太空旅客，而他更豪氣地包下所有座位，「（登月）是我的終身夢想，我會跟來自全球6至8名藝術家一起前往月球」。前澤友作最快將於2023年實現夢想，未知目前跟他拍拖的日劇《首相閣下的料理人》25歲女星剛力彩芽，屆時可會成為其中一名旅伴？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00007/1537254481171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00007%2F1537254481171&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d3537aee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00007%2F1537254481171&h=f8940d4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00007/1537254481171</a>"},{"pid":"398fed851d2466f2e72bb26cc7b990fbafc9a50f","tid":826417,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c769159331e75e7b461d2bbdae3a1054a0d65a","tid":826417,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"未散先算啦，仲有幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}